### GET ALL POSTS - Público
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts

### GET POST POR ID - Público
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts/1

### CREAR POST - Usuario/Admin (requiere JWT)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Post de prueba",
  "contenido": "Contenido de prueba para el post",
  "categoria_ids": [1]
}

### EDITAR POST - Solo Autor/Admin
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Post editado",
  "contenido": "Contenido actualizado"
}

### ELIMINAR POST - Solo Autor/Admin
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### GET COMENTARIOS DE UN POST
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts/1/comments

### CREAR COMENTARIO - Usuario/Admin
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts/1/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contenido": "Este es un comentario de prueba"
}

### ELIMINAR COMENTARIO - Autor/Moderator/Admin
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

